# SAMSUNG PMIC

config DRV_SAMSUNG_PMIC
	tristate "Samsung PMIC common and sysfs system"
	depends on I2C
	help
	 This driver supports a Samsung PMIC sysfs amd common.

config REGULATOR_S2MPS25
	tristate "Samsung S2MPS25 voltage regulator"
	depends on MFD_S2MPS25
	help
	  This driver supports a Samsung S2MPS25 voltage output regulator
	  via I2C bus. S2MPS25 is comprised of high efficient Buck converters
	  including Dual-Phase Buck converter, Buck-Boost converter, various LDOs.

config REGULATOR_S2MPS26
